metadata.name: Satodelic Phase I
metadata.description: Satodelic is a visual journey that explores the creative and personal process, understanding that there is no evolution without resistance. Each piece is a unique expression of the path towards realization and the discovery of human potential. Inspired by the Japanese word 'Satori', which means awakening and profound understanding, this collection invites you to discover new horizons of exploration and growth in the small and big moments of life.
